✅ Official OSUVOX Avatar Minter.


⭐ After minting you will receive an OSUBOX that will turn into an Osuvox Avatar after a 24 hour period.


ℹ️ For more information about the Osuvox and its metaverse avatar, join our phenomenal [Discord community](https://discord.gg/3uzNabHvGM) or visit our [website](https://osuvox.io/). Click here to see the [Osuvox collection](https://opensea.io/collection/osuvox-metaverse-avatars).
